name: Sound of Fractures - No One Knows Me Like You (Green Ring Remix)

attributes.trait_type: No One Knows Me Like You (Green Ring Remix)

metadata.description:
Green Ring is a producer based in New Hampshire making emotional and melodic house music. “My goal with every piece of music is to take you somewhere new. I want your mind to drift off from the day to day when you listen."

I’ve been a big fan of Jamie’s music since I first came across it earlier this year, so I was very excited to be tapped for this remix. The idea came together pretty quickly as the original song has some amazing stems to work from. I used a lot of the vocal textures from Scott and just tried to contextualize them in a new way by changing up the chords and adding some new rhythms. I ended up with an organic/ambient house song that I’m really happy with. I hope you enjoy and thank you so much for the support!
metadata.name: No One Knows Me Like You (Green Ring Remix) #1
